This map is in beta and a very big stretch out.
Me and a couple guys in my clan thought it would be fun to race barrels in our server one day.
Thought it would be a fun map so i made one.
There are probably a lot of mistakes and error's.
Please leave all comments on your thoughts for this.
Also if you would like to see something new i am willing to work with yea on it.
I hope this hits big because i would love to make more.

I know i do not have a great screen shot as of now but as soon as i do i will post one.

So a basic rundown of the map. t and ct have a race to the goals with some balls :D (YOU DIRTY MINDED FUC*s)
If t gets the ball in the goal first Ct will be slayed and both balls will be sent back to start. T will be sent to spawn and the race shall start over agin.
